Okay now I'm done :)

YangYang said spent his bday in the midst of working! After he got home, he slept, everyone was at the dorm and Renjun & Chenle came to the dorm as well! 

He played games a bit w/ Chenle and then they ordered cake, sang "happy birthday" and then they went back to practice.
YangYang said it's kind of crazy that he's 20 now, bc in the past when he wrote his age it would always start w/ "1"
YangYang: "Thank you so much to everyone for spending my birthday with me. I hope that you can spend my birthday together with me next year too"
I watched back the live and YangYang was specifically pointing out that Hendery wasn't talking because his throat hasn't been feeling that great recently!

+ then YY won again. And then for the last round, YY said that if Hendery lost, he would have to post on Weibo saying "Liu YangYang's basketball skills are so so so so so so much better than Hendery's"

YY: "There's no way I could let go of that opportunity, so I won again" 😀👍

+
super pleased with himself, so he said, 'okay, let's do one more round!' If I lose this round, I'll treat you to hotpot until you're full. After I heard that, I won :)"

Then after THAT, they did another round & if YY won, Hendery would treat him to bbq until YY was full, and
+

+
to a meal. "At first I won, and then I won again!" And then for the third round, YangYang suggested that if Hendery won, it would negate the YY's first 2 wins, but if YY won again, it would be double. 

Hendery won the 3rd round, so they're back to 0-0. And then "Hendery was
+

YangYang said "ah, there's something I do wanna brag about" He's talking about the basketball bet (Weibo post)!

He went to play 1-on-1 basketball w/ Hendery and they thought bc it was just 1-on-1, it's pretty boring, so they said that whoever won would treat the other person
+

YangYang also said he's gotten closer to Jeno recently! Because these days, he's been filming with Jeno so they've gotten closer & chat w/ each other!

He initially thought Jeno was gonna be kind of introverted, but after getting to know him, he's a very fun/amusing person!

Hahaha YangYang "Part 2? I've never given a spoiler, right? I have to keep it that way. No spoiler"

And now we're back to my first live tweet translation about darker hair colors!

YangYang says Misfit was like the first time filming an MV with other people! Bc even for the promo, it didn't feel like an MV, but with Misfit it really felt like they had chemistry bc they're all rappers!

He says he also learned a lot from the other members in Misfit :)

YangYang: "Oh right! Guys, aren't the songs on this album super good?" 

He says his favorite songs are "Nectar! And also... Nectar, Misfit, and Make A Wish is also really good~"

Hahahahha YangYang was like "is there anyone watching my live in class?"

And then he went "BALALALALALALAA TEACHER THERE'S SOMEONE HERE WATCHING MY LIVE QUICKLY CATCH THEM AND LECTURE THEM-"
Hahahahahahaha YangYang said him and the plushie were a couple look 😂 https://t.co/5RSqU0zo18

He recently bought a new plushie!

When he bought it he thought it was like (pic 2) size big bc "you can't tell how big it is just from the picture bc I bought it online, who knew that it would be like this size when it arrived" 😂 https://t.co/1AHJLHTOB6
YangYang says they have an electric mosquito swatter but they don't really use it. It's by Xiaojun's bed but it's basically just decor at this point and he rarely sees Xiaojun bring it out and use it

YangYang says there's tons of mosquitoes these days and that sometimes they're so loud that they wake up him up at night

He says he HATES the buzzing sounds of mosquitoes and that you have to wake up to kill them and it's super annoying

The glasses that YangYang wore yesterday in his Insta Story were gifted to him by Hendery for his birthday! They're blue light glasses so he wears them now whenever he plays games :)

He just finished practicing and says he's going to watch "From Home" unit's live later!

Okay replaying the live so I can catch the beginning!

YangYang said he was wearing a hat because his hair's super messy right now.

YangYang's calling for Bella but she isn't coming haha "give your gege some face"

"Yeah, she isn't giving me any face"

Ok he's leaving now because he's going to hang with Bella! He thinks Bella's kind of tired and that if he keeps making sounds she might bite him.

End of live!

YangYang was calling for Leon but Leon was ignoring him. "I think Leon doesn't know his own name. Either that or he just chooses to ignore me."

He says Bella doesn't usually bark at home! Only when other people come.

YangYang also said that he saw all the birthday projects that fans prepared and that he was super touched by all of them!

Hendery came in but he didn't talk. YangYang says Hendery hasn't been feeling super well/is quite tired probably bc he/they've been practicing a lot lately

YangYang also says that Louis has gotten skinnier recently! He said maybe Louis understood that they were calling him "fat boy" in Cantonese so he got skinnier. Either that or the reason is because Louis can't compete w/ Leon bc Leon takes all the food bc he eats super quickly

YangYang says the cats have been really cute recently too! Bc Ten has been buying them clothes haha and because Louis kind of has a stoic face, when they dress Louis up he looks like he's forced to wear the clothes 😂

YangYang says Bella's been really cute recently though. She doesn't like staying in her cage and when they put her in the cage, she starts whimpering. But when they let her out she doesn't do much either she just lies in a different position

He says she's a princess :)

Hahahahahaa YangYang said the acoustic foam (the failed soundproof stuff that they stuck on the door) has all been ripped to shreds by Bella hahahaha

"Is Bella in a rebellious phase?"
YY: Bella's always been in a rebellious phase

+ joined. He also said Sungchan has improved a lot since they were trainees together

He also said Shotaro is SO GOOD at dancing and that he wants to learn from him!

Yangyang said he hasn't bought the Resonance albums yet, but his family has but none of them pulled him. He said his mom pulled Hendery and Taeyong-hyung

He says it's quite interesting that Sungchan is technically his senior bc Sungchan was already at the company when he +

#YANGYANG Yizhibo Live!

YangYang said for the title track for pt. 2 that he's in, since it's retro hip-hop, they've all gone back to darker hair colors since there weren't very flashy hair colors back then!
